[h1]Aurora[/h1]
[i]A content mod for tModLoader.[/i]

Aurora introduces unique, fantasy-inspired content and quality-of-life features that seamlessly blend with the vanilla game, enhancing the overall immersive experience.

[hr][/hr] 
[h2]Community[/h2]
[h3]Support[/h3]
Require in-game assistance? Join our [url=https://discord.gg/WzpbgbUkKe]Discord server[/url] to ask questions and chat with other players and the development team.

[h3]Contributing[/h3]
Interested in contributing? Join our [url=https://discord.gg/WzpbgbUkKe]Discord server[/url] to get started and stay informed.

[hr][/hr] 
[h2]Troubleshooting[/h2]
If you encounter any issues while using Aurora, please check our [url=https://github.com/shnakamura/Aurora/issues]Issues[/url] section to see if the problem has already been reported or addressed. If not, you can open a new issue describing the problem in detail through one of our issue templates.

